T_f: 该应用程序的一位发言人提供了隐私功能，以帮助用户避免此类问题。

S_s: The celebrities did use their megaphones to promote masks.
S_f: The celebrities did use their megaphones to promote masks and social media.
T_s: 名人确实用他们的扩音器来宣传口罩。
T_f: 名人确实使用他们的扩音器来宣传面具和社交媒体。

S_s: Many companies are conducting road shows, holding national and regional conferences, and organizing events.
S_f: Many companies are conducting road shows, holding national and regional conferences, and organizing events and incentive trips.
T_s: 许多公司都在进行路演、举办国家和地区会议以及组织活动。
T_f: 许多公司都在进行路演、举办国家和地区会议，并组织活动和奖励旅游。

S_s: Also this year the BBC announced an organisation-wide voluntary redundancy scheme.
S_f: Also this year the BBC announced an organisation-wide voluntary redundancy scheme to help it meet its stringent savings target.
T_s: 同样在今年，BBC 宣布了一项全组织范围内的自愿裁员计划。
T_f: 今年，BBC 还宣布了一项全组织范围内的自愿裁员计划，以帮助其实现严格的储蓄目标。

S_s: Crowd numbers will be reduced and all those present will be able to provide their name.
S_f: Crowd numbers will be reduced and all those present will be able to provide their name, surname and mobile phone information.
T_s: 人群数量将减少，所有在场的人都可以提供他们的名字。
T_f: 人群数量将减少，所有在场的人都可以提供他们的名字、姓氏和手机信息。

S_s: Coffeehouses helped spread modern democracy, and the Enlightenment.
S_f: Coffeehouses helped spread modern democracy, and the Enlightenment and the periodical literature.
T_s: 咖啡馆帮助传播了现代民主和启蒙运动。
